{"word":"πάλαι","slug":"πάλαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>πάλαι</el></b> [<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ etym.\">etym.</a> complex] <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ adv.\">adv.</a> in <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ ref.\">ref.</a> to time past and variously nuanced<b><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> much earlier than the present time <b>long ago <a href='B:470 11:21'>Mt 11:21</a>; <a href='B:650 1:1'>Hb 1:1</a>; <a href='B:720 1:1'>Jd 4</a>; (in the) past <a href='B:680 1:9'>2 Pt 1:9</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> relatively close to the present time <b>for a while <a href='B:480 6:47'>Mk 6:47</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ v.l.\">v.l.</a>; already <a href='B:480 15:44'>15:44</a>; all this time/while <a href='B:540 12:19'>2 Cor 12:19</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:Πακατιανός\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:παλαιός\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}